CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE [dbo].[ext_DIM_CUSTOMER] WITH (
        LOCATION = 'DIM_CUSTOMER/Archive',
        DATA_SOURCE = [eds_tx-halfen-2-dwh],
        FILE_FORMAT = [eff_Parquet]
) AS
SELECT
    *
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK './DIM_CUSTOMER/In/2023/01/13/DIM_CUSTOMER_2023_01_13_04_32_29_567.parquet',
        FORMAT = 'PARQUET'
    ) AS [result]
WHERE Company NOT IN ('5307', '5309', '5310', '5325')
